---
title: Chermoula & Sumac Cannellini Bean Quesadillas with Plant-Based Cheese & Sour Cream
description: Cannellini beans, gooey plant-based cheese and Middle-Eastern spices unite to make a hearty and delicious filling for these
quesadillas. Simply spoon the cheesy filling onto tortillas, fold them in half and bake. Easy cheesy dinner coming right up!
